file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: "API"
  version: "1.0.0"
  contact:
    name: Contact Name
    email: contact@example.com
    url: https://example.com/
tags:
  - name: Metadata
    description: Metadata related requests
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: things#index
      summary: Get metadata from the root of the API
      tags: ["Metadata"]
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required: [hello]
                properties:
                  hello:
                    type: string
